ct","friendlyName":"方言转换器","friendlyNameEn":"@UtpalJayNadiger-tf-dialect","description":"基于TensorFlow Lite的轻量级方言识别与转写模型，支持粤语、闽南语等中文方言语音到文本转换，适用于边缘设备。","descriptionEn":"","category":"other","tags":["语音识别","方言处理","边缘AI","TensorFlow Lite","本地推理"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"/absolute/path/to/tf-dialect/dist/index.js","securityScore":59,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":true,"installMethod":"npm","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/UtpalJayNadiger/tf-dialect","source":"modelscope","configHint":"需预加载方言模型文件（约15MB），不依赖云服务","isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["方言保护","智能硬件","老年友好交互","本地化语音助手"]},{"serverId":"marsdes-mcpdify","friendlyName":"Dify参数管理器","friendlyNameEn":"dify参数获取","description":"专为Dify平台设计的MCP参数注入与安全加载服务，支持环境变量、.env、YAML多模式配置解析。","descriptionEn":"# 获取dify参数\n\n在使用Dify时，您可能需要获取某些配置参数来完成特定任务。以下是如何获取这些参数的方法。\n\n## 通过环境变量获取\n\nDify支持通过环境变量来设置和获取配置参数。这是推荐的方式，因为它可以确保您的敏感信息不会被硬编码到代码中。\n\n### 示例\n\nbash\nexport DIFY_API_KEY=your_api_key_here\n\n\n然后，在您的应用程序中，您可以这样读取它：\n\npython\nimport os\n\napi_key = os.getenv('DIFY_API_KEY')\nprint(f\"API Key: {api_key}\")\n\n\n## 使用配置文件\n\n除了环境变量外，您还可以选择使用配置文件（如`.env`或`.yaml`）来管理您的Dify参数。\n\n### .env 文件示例\n\n创建一个名为`.env`的文件，并添加如下内容：\n\n\nDIFY_API_KEY=your_api_key_here\n\n\n接着，在Python项目中安装`python-dotenv`库并加载该文件：\n\npython\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\nimport os\n\nload_dotenv()  # 加载 .env 文件\napi_key = os.getenv('DIFY_API_KEY')\nprint(f\"API Key: {api_key}\")\n\n\n### YAML 配置文件示例\n\n如果您更喜欢YAML格式，可以创建一个`config.yaml`文件：\n\nyaml\ndify:\n  api_key: your_api_key_here\n\n\n使用Python的`PyYAML`库来解析这个文件：\n\npython\nimport yaml\n\nwith open('config.yaml', 'r') as file:\n    config = yaml.safe_load(file)\n\napi_key = config['dify']['api_key']\nprint(f\"API Key: {api_key}\")\n\n\n## 官方文档链接\n\n更多关于如何配置Dify的信息，请参考[官方文档](https://docs.dify.ai/)。\n\n以上就是获取Dify参数的基本方法。根据您的具体需求选择合适的方式来管理和访问这些参数吧！","category":"filesystem","tags":["Dify集成","配置管理","环境变量","安全注入","YAML解析"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"marsdes-mcpdify","securityScore":59,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":false,"installMethod":"none","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/marsDes/difymcp.git","source":"modelscope","configHint":"兼容Dify Cloud与Dify Self-hosted部署，需确保MCP客户端与Dify后端网络互通","envSchema":{"Password":{"description":"","type":"string"}},"envRequired":["Password"],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["低代码集成","Dify自动化部署","AI应用配置中心"]},{"serverId":"stonecoming-doc-tools-mcp-test","friendlyName":"石来文档","friendlyNameEn":"stonecoming-doc-tools-mcp-test","description":"面向企业知识库的文档元数据提取与索引服务，支持自定义字段标注与版本快照比对。","descriptionEn":"","category":"other","tags":["文档元数据","知识图谱","版本比对","企业知识库","MCP协议"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"@puchunjie/doc-tools-mcp","securityScore":59,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":true,"installMethod":"npm","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/puchunjie/doc-tools-mcp","source":"modelscope","configHint":"默认嵌入 SQLite 存储；生产环境可对接 PostgreSQL","envSchema":{},"envRequired":[],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":true,"capabilities":["内部知识管理","合规文档归档","研发文档治理"]},{"serverId":"@kenforthewin-docker-mcp-server","friendlyName":"赢者容器","friendlyNameEn":"@kenforthewin-docker-mcp-server","description":"面向 CI/CD 流水线的 Docker 运行时 MCP 封装服务，支持构建缓存复用与镜像签名验证。","descriptionEn":"","category":"other","tags":["CI/CD","Docker构建","镜像签名","流水线集成","安全合规"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"@kenforthewin-docker-mcp-server","securityScore":59,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":false,"installMethod":"none","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/kenforthewin/docker-mcp-server","source":"mode